Each is the best video I could find. A few are available in larger files
but the video quality difference is neglible to none.(on a 22&quot; -1080p monitor)

Also several are readily available here , but I included them anyway
because ,after all , this IS a filmography.

After the title I've added the name of the uploader I got the video file from.
(where I could). 

I've deleted all non English audio tracks (&amp; added a few to 
the ones that only had foreign audio). I almost gave up on finding an complete
English track for &quot;1971 Someone Behind the Door&quot;

Added a 2m58s clip of &quot;1952 Battle Zone&quot; (can't find whole movie)

Added a trailer of Mitzi Gaynor's &quot;1952 Bloodhounds of Broadway&quot;. WOW 
(can't find whole movie)

** I have a significantly better copy of &quot;1965 Guns of Diablo&quot; with
Russian audio.I've added an English audio track to it but I can't syncronise 
it because the English copies I have all have a 15 second chunk cut out near 
the 9 minute mark. I don't know how to work around that.

** I have a dvd copy of &quot;1955 Target Zero&quot; but the audio tracks are Dutch 
and Russian.Haven't found any English audio yet.

The total size of this filmography is approxomatly 108gb.I've split it up 
into 3 torrents of fairly equal size (GB wise , not number of movies)

In the early ones Charles Bronson plays supporting roles to bit parts to 
uncredited parts.

I didn't put in any effort to find subtitles or HQ posters , just added 
what I came accross

I thought this filmography would be a lot easier to put together than my
